Package: cvir
Title: Content Validity Index (CVI) Calculation Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jesica", "Formoso", , "jesica.formoso@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3062-4036"))
Description: Provides functions to calculate the Content Validity Index (CVI) 
    for individual items and entire scales based on expert ratings. Includes 
    both item-level CVI calculations and scale-level indices using average and 
    universal agreement methods. Based on Yusoff MSB (2019). ABC of content validation 
    and content validity index calculation. Education in Medicine Journal. 11(2)
    doi 10.21315/eimj2019.11.2.6.
